# Kairos Blog - Agent Guide

## Project Overview

Kairos Blog (中文名: Kairos博客) is a personal blog website built with modern frontend technologies. It is a static single-page application (SPA) designed for GitHub Pages deployment.

**Project Purpose**: A personal technical blog for sharing programming insights, learning experiences, and life reflections. The author is a Network Engineering undergraduate student at Henan University (河南大学).

**Language**: The UI is primarily in Chinese (Simplified), with some English technical terms.

---

## Technology Stack

| Category | Technology | Version |
|----------|------------|---------|
| Framework | React | ^19.1.1 |
| Language | TypeScript | ~5.8.3 |
| Build Tool | Vite | ^7.1.2 |
| Routing | React Router DOM | ^7.8.2 |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS | ^3.4.17 |
| CSS Processor | PostCSS + Autoprefixer | ^10.4.21 |
| Linting | ESLint + typescript-eslint | ^9.33.0 |

